{"id":"5c3c04dfbe23a10017086e2f","title":"node.jsのmongooseでnestしたobjectをpopulateする - dev.jgs.me","image":null,"created":1380034800,"updated":1601235935,"lines":[{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d809","text":"node.jsのmongooseでnestしたobjectをpopulateする - dev.jgs.me","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d80c","text":"`node.js` の `mongoose` でネストしたドキュメントを `populate` したいときの話。","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d80d","text":"","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d80e","text":"`3.6` 系から `populate` の仕様が変わるようで、以前のように","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d80f","text":"","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d810","text":"code:_","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d811","text":" Document.find().populate(\"comment.author\").exec (err, docs)->","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d812","text":"","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d813","text":"のようなコードでは `populate` できなくなった。代わりに","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d814","text":"","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d815","text":"code:_","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d816","text":" Document.find().populate(\"comment\").exec (err, docs)->","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d817","text":"   User.populate docs,","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d818","text":"     path: \"comment.author\"","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d819","text":"   , (err, docs)->","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d81a","text":"","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d81b","text":"のように書いてやると当該部分が `populate` される。ちょっとややこしいなあ。","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d81c","text":"","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d81d","text":"[https://github.com/LearnBoost/mongoose/issues/1377 https://github.com/LearnBoost/mongoose/issues/1377]","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d81e","text":"","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d81f","text":"[* original: http://dev.jgs.me/2013/09/25/nested-mongoose]","created":1380034800,"updated":1380034800},{"id":"5c3c04df4ade4d0000c9d820","text":"#20130925 #0925","created":1380034800,"updated":1601235932},{"id":"5f70ebdc4ade4d000063f7df","text":"","created":1601235933,"updated":1601235933}]}